OL,6,FA spokesperson for the care centre
OL,7,Fsaid: "We want to extend our sincere
OL,8,Fapologies to the families affected by
OL,9,Fthis situation and are committed to
OL,10,Fworking hard to rebuild their trust.
OL,11,FThe safety, dignity, and wellbeing of
OL,12,Feveryone we support are, and have
OL,13,Falways been, our top priorities, and
OL,14,Fwe want to reassure everyone we work
OL,15,Fwith, and the entire community, that
OL,16,Fwe remain fully committed to the
OL,17,Fhighest standards of care.
