OL,3,CThree staff members at care home
OL,4,Carrested after allegations of violence
OL,6,F"We were shocked to discover the
OL,7,Falleged incidents, as they do not
OL,8,Freflect the values we uphold or the
OL,9,Flevel of care we strive to provide
OL,10,Fevery day. As soon as we were made
OL,11,Faware, we took immediate action, and
OL,12,Fwe are cooperating fully with all
OL,13,Frelevant authorities to ensure a
OL,14,Fcomprehensive and transparent
OL,15,Finvestigation.
