OL,3,CThree staff members at care home
OL,4,Carrested after allegations of violence
OL,6,F"We are absolutely committed to doing
OL,7,Feverything we can to prevent any
OL,8,Fsimilar situations in the future. We
OL,9,Fhave always maintained strict
OL,10,Fprotocols, including a rigorous hiring
OL,11,Fprocess and thorough training to
OL,12,Fensure a compassionate, professional
OL,13,Fteam. However, we are now enhancing
OL,14,Fthese measures by working closely with
OL,15,Fexternal experts to review and
OL,16,Fstrengthen our monitoring systems.
OL,17,FThis includes more frequent
OL,18,Funannounced inspections and
OL,19,Findependent audits to provide an added
OL,20,Flayer of oversight. In addition, we
OL,21,Fare expanding our team's training to
OL,22,Fensure any concerns are reported to
OL,23,Fmanagement immediately.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
