OL,6,F"Our team is fully dedicated to
OL,7,Fproviding a safe, respectful, and
OL,8,Fnurturing environment, and we will
OL,9,Fcontinue to do everything possible to
OL,10,Fensure that our residents receive the
OL,11,Fcompassionate, high-quality care they
OL,12,Fdeserve. Robust safeguarding measures
OL,13,Fare in place, and we remain unwavering
OL,14,Fin our commitment to the ongoing care
OL,15,Fand safety of our residents."
